cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is about a Deep Reinforcement Learning algorithm that uses Experience Replay to improve the agent's performance. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The algorithm also deals with a nondeterministic environment, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
